{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2d19dd6b9d","title":"和蒙古人民革命党代表团的谈话和印发谈话记录的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0bb0f6ae91","index":1,"year":1956,"month":12,"day":null,"articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"62f049557f","index":0,"year":1956,"month":9,"day":null,"articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji37","name":"毛泽东全集第37卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/37-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji37":{"comments":[{"id":"5c6fc7c777","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"泽登巴尔，当时任蒙古人民共和国部长会议主席。14]桑布，当时任蒙古人民共和国大人民呼拉尔主席团主席。"},{"id":"f337ba59f3","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"集二线，指内蒙古自治区的集宁至二连浩特的铁路。这条铁路北出国境同蒙古人民共和国的铁路相接。"},{"id":"477c29929d","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"尚昆，即杨尚昆，当时任中共中央书记处候补书记、中央办公厅主任。中共中央于1956年12月16日将毛泽东的谈话记录发给各省市委、自治区党委、西藏工委、驻蒙古大使馆。"}],"contents":[{"id":"50dc43a7bd","type":"title","text":"和蒙古人民革命党代表团的谈话和印发谈话记录的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"5c6fc7c777","type":"paragraph","text":"一谈话记录","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"f337ba59f3","type":"paragraph","text":"时间：一九五六年九月二十四日","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"477c29929d","type":"paragraph","text":"参加人：蒙方：达姆巴川（团长）、曾德、奥其尔巴特（大","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"e58f3af940","type":"paragraph","text":"使）、哈什冈白、策热布桑巴","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"070edf84e8","type":"paragraph","text":"中方：王称祥","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"7e249b4922","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东（以下简称毛）：这几天你们很累了吧","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"029f660f1d","type":"paragraph","text":"达姆巴（以下简称达）：不，不累，我们很舒服。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"cff74d3ee4","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：蒙古同志是好同志，好朋友。你们是友好的国家，友好的党！","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"f90826f0ca","type":"paragraph","text":"（接着主席就问候泽登巴尔同志）","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"f93b2e1ef0","type":"paragraph","text":"达：他很好，他跟桑布用同志向您问候呢！","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"c38716a1a9","type":"paragraph","text":"I1]达姆巴，当时任蒙古人民革命党中央委员会第一书记。","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"d8afa4f7d7","type":"paragraph","text":"主森祥，当时任中共中央对外联络部部长。","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"4f3a238ae3","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：谢谢！请你们替我向他们问候！","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"8fa087e44a","type":"paragraph","text":"达：谢谢！我们感谢你们对我们的接助。","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"88ad2cb17e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：不，不要这样！中国是个大国，这是我们的义务，是你们的权利。我经常听到你们这样讲，同时经常看到文件上也这样写，我觉得心里不舒服。我们应该尽到自己的责任，因为三百年来我们的祖先曾剥削过你们、压追过你们，他们曾留下了不少的债务，因此，今天我们要还这些债务。过去我国国内少数民族也同样受过压道，我们对他们也要还债，这是我们的义务。","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"af410493d3","type":"paragraph","text":"我国藏族人口的一百二十万人直接属于拉萨，其他一百万人口分布于青海、云南、四川、甘肃等地。蒙古的宗教情况怎样？喇嘛多不多？总人口多少？达：过去很多，现在非常少了。在革命初期，有些喇嘛干过坏事情，将他们处理了。有一些参加了劳动以及其他工作。现在还有极少数的喇嘛。我国总人口八十万。","index":16,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"f39a0452e4","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：蒙古工农业的发展情况如何？","index":17,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"1c846e0b34","type":"paragraph","text":"达：革命前我们是个很落后的国家，在革命的年代里，由于苏联的热情帮助，我国人民在工业方面、牧高业方面以及文化教育方面都有了很好的进展。","index":18,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"027fc3720c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：蒙古农业也很发展了吧","index":19,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"6175f25878","type":"paragraph","text":"达：今年刚开始发展农业。","index":20,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"cc32f8d156","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：水够不够？","index":21,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"a57779172a","type":"paragraph","text":"达：在我国，水是很缺之的。","index":22,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"6c47b26d50","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：雨量如何","index":23,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"880d8e5b1c","type":"paragraph","text":"达：平均年雨量是一百二十至三百毫米（其中森林地带是三百毫米，而沙漠地区是一百二十毫米）。","index":24,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"27a3a94e51","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：打井怎样","index":25,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"cb7962a78c","type":"paragraph","text":"达：沙漠地区打井困难。","index":26,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"55600da64f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：那么，建设一些蓄水库，储下水来，以供使用，这样不可以吗？","index":27,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"e7b24ae724","type":"paragraph","text":"达：在沙漠地带很困难，水储不下，很快渗入地下。","index":28,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"75c383cbb4","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：你们境内有哪些大河流","index":29,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"ff619df76b","type":"paragraph","text":"达：色楞河、鄂嫩河、克鲁伦河等。","index":30,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"34a4d54297","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：向西北方向流去的是哪一条河","index":31,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"718989cd0e","type":"paragraph","text":"达：鄂嫩河、克鲁伦河。","index":32,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"fa9137019e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：蒙古历史、文化的发源地是哪里","index":33,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"35ee83fd33","type":"paragraph","text":"达：鄂嫩河、克鲁伦河一带。","index":34,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"10893237c3","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：你们不可以在这些河流上建筑一些水闸、水库、蓄洪沟等工程吗？","index":35,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"13f80d6ced","type":"paragraph","text":"达：人民和我们都迫切要求那样做，但力量达不到。","index":36,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"8bc3b3c2a5","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：现在我们也有些困难。但几年之后，我们在这方面帮助你们。","index":37,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"2991723f3f","type":"paragraph","text":"达：谢谢。","index":38,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"d1e5b08e66","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：今年河北闹水灾，三千万亩农田遭到了水。中国的水利工作，至今还没有能够很大发展，再有十年之久可能解决。不过，我们在这方面对你们的援助，用不了等十年之久。","index":39,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"f63ac7663b","type":"paragraph","text":"达：去年你们给予了我们很多的援助，派了一万三千工人和技术员，这在工业和其他建设方面起了推动作用。并且今年还给了无偿的一亿六千万卢布。因此，蒙古老百姓非常欢欣鼓舞。","index":40,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"5bb8d458f7","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：不，不，上边已经说过，这是我们的义务。那些数目是太少了，你们一提，我就觉得恢愧。","index":41,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"f0c77e606d","type":"paragraph","text":"达：集二线川对我国的发展起了很大的作用。","index":42,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"fbbf1c885c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：蒙古的农业现在怎样","index":43,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"7b51651699","type":"paragraph","text":"达：现在较过去有了一些发展，但由于人力缺乏，很大一块土地至今还未开星。","index":44,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"a94c0dd8b2","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：这样不好，应该开荒。你们定居了吗","index":45,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"a9b2edb378","type":"paragraph","text":"达：定居对我国农牧业发展，有很大好处，但现在还未定居下来。","index":46,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"f7252ff7b5","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：这不是一下子办得到的，要逐步地办到，因为一个地方的草，是有限制的。我国有的省也有类似这样的情况。定居下来，还可以种菜，种庄称，这样人口才能增加","index":47,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"b39de68822","type":"paragraph","text":"达：对！（指曾德说）他是国家计划委员会的主任。您的这些建议，对我国将来的计划工作有很大的帮助。","index":48,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"0b2de2e1be","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：发展农业、牧畜业，首先要发展水利工作，这里包括水闸、蓄水库、水沟等工程。另一方面，牧草是很重要的，对你们来讲，“草就是油”。因此，你们应当培植牧草，应当采用深耕的方法，这样牧草就能长得又高又多，然后定居下来就有条件了","index":49,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"43879c2b97","type":"paragraph","text":"达：是的！我们重视您的这些谈话。","index":50,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"3c91966444","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：你们可以早一些开始水利工程的准备工作。这方面包括地质勘察工作、人力、物力等等，而财力还不算那么重要，最重要、最要紧的是人力。","index":51,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"d16db68e60","type":"paragraph","text":"你们应该先着手进行最迫切需要的工作。例如，由乌兰巴托到西部国境，这一段路的中间，你们修了一条近代化的大马路，但很少用它。这是不很需要的。","index":52,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"ce03c5fe72","type":"paragraph","text":"达：中华人民共和国成立以来只有七年之久。在这以前，我们两国人民不大来往。虽然我国革命成功已有三十五年，但由于我国过去很落后，所以在这三十五年内未能很好地发展起来（虽然有成绩）。因此我国工农业可以说是没有很好地发展。","index":53,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"a0481320ef","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：你们应该自给自足","index":54,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"fb7948362d","type":"paragraph","text":"达：现在许多日用品都不能自己生产。","index":55,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"5142715a6d","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：这是不好的，应该扩大这方面的工业","index":56,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"11b40a2325","type":"paragraph","text":"达：日本帝国主义对我国的侵略，也影响了这一方面的发展。","index":57,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"dcc7cda033","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：你们还有多少军队？","index":58,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"5891820f14","type":"paragraph","text":"达：将近一师。","index":59,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"958b2aafd9","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：这已够用了。现在，你们周围没有敌人","index":60,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"b9a65ac4a9","type":"paragraph","text":"达：现在我们正在将这支部队的复员人员培养成为司机、建筑工人等。","index":61,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"6cfc585b74","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：这是很好的。这是生产军！那么文字怎样呢","index":62,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"80067b9e87","type":"paragraph","text":"达：现在都用新（俄）文字，成年人都已识字了。","index":63,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"fe24c829c4","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：很好，内蒙古也正在这样做","index":64,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"dab591b343","type":"paragraph","text":"达：据说是那样。在文字方面，我们也可以帮助内蒙古。","index":65,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"90638695aa","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：对，很需要这样。你们跟内蒙古有直接联系吗","index":66,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"dcb5898405","type":"paragraph","text":"达：现在没有直接联系呢！只是通过中央取得联系。","index":67,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"eb7e3a0c4e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：不需要直接联系吗","index":68,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"01c213bd32","type":"paragraph","text":"达：需要直接联系，但未办正式手续。","index":69,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"2238bee8ae","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：你们可以办的。你们可以到内蒙古建立自己的领事馆。这样做，用不了什么费用！你们从自己的大使馆抽出几个人来，就可以了。苏联也这样办的。在天津、上海、沈阳、广州等地都有他们的领事馆。","index":70,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"ac5b306025","type":"paragraph","text":"不过，上述这些事，是我个人的说法，也许不正确，因为我未与政府、外交部负责人商量；同样，你们也是未与自己的政府商量过。但我认为，这些事情是能够实现的。","index":71,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"9326794b4a","type":"paragraph","text":"达：谢谢！历史上的“债务”，我们连想也没想过。我们只是感谢你们。","index":72,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"8a0b7ac669","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：不！要还债的，这是我们在追还祖先们的债务。","index":73,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"41a004e746","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：你们蒙古族是第三个民族。第一个民族是固奴。它占了新疆、黄河北部的土地，有的已渡过了黄河。第二个民族是突脉，它占领了阿美尼亚、保加利亚、南斯拉夫、埃及、希腊等十几个民族，建立了大帝国。但这一民族后来被蒙古族打败了。因此，蒙古是第三个民族。我们至今还没有搞清你们的祖先的来源。是不是在西伯利亚？","index":74,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"93103bc491","type":"paragraph","text":"奥其尔巴特：唤！据说是那样！","index":75,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"d0c187f9d5","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：西伯利亚那里曾有一个高车族，据说他们都坐在高大的车子上。高车族是不是你们的祖先？","index":76,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"a0e4ec8ca7","type":"paragraph","text":"达：老人们都说，古代的祖先搬家时都用很高的车拉上所有的东西。","index":77,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"85f6003fbf","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：你们有没有关于这一方面的记载","index":78,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"af59a2c7bd","type":"paragraph","text":"达：关于十二世纪以前的记载，现在还没有，十三世纪以后的有些记载。这一方面的工作苏联帮助着我们。十三世纪以前的蒙古历史，跟中国历史有着密切的关系，因此，将来我们在这方面，可能还要跟你们一起进行研究。","index":79,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"18d4eee27f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：很好，今天我们谈了许多有关历史的事情。","index":80,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"0d6141ff4f","type":"paragraph","text":"达：我们的前途很宽广，因为有苏联和中国的兄弟般的援助。今后，我们更要好好努力工作。","index":81,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"fc090c4c0c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：应该好好发展。","index":82,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"1517357feb","type":"paragraph","text":"达：我再一次表达我们内心的感激，你们对我们的援助是兄弟般的伟大的援助。我们不能把它当做“债务”来看待。","index":83,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"6bc8ad7958","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：但我们是这样想的。我们同任何国家都以平等共处，过去我们压追了你们，因此现在要向你们认错。不仅对你们这样，而且对国内少数民族也是这样的。过去，我们压追了他们，因此，如果我们现在不认错，就不能根除大汉族主义思想，实现民族平等。这是有根据的，这不是漂亮话。是不是？过去我们压追过你们，但你们现在一句忽言都没有。我们给你们的援助是小小的，这是在还债，不是援助。这样才能互相信赖。你们说是援助，这也好，你们这样说也表示平等。","index":84,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"b367c6ac4a","type":"paragraph","text":"达：我们对你们所给予我们的过去的和将来的一切援助表示感谢！中蒙两国劳动人民一向是友好的，反动阶级所干的事情是另一回事。","index":85,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"976131173b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：有些中国工人去蒙古了。你们应该对他们进行宣传工作，以免他们犯大汉族主义思想的毛病，以免他们称主称霸","index":86,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"f2b1732c7e","type":"paragraph","text":"那里的中国工人或工作人员如果犯错误，你们应该向我们反映。","index":87,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"fc9c6f359d","type":"paragraph","text":"达：大多数的人都很好，少数人虽有时犯毛病，但那也不是有意识的。同时，谁都会有一些缺点的。","index":88,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"079d3c9ba4","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：应该教育他们，如果有人犯严重错误，就应当依法处分。你们应以主人翁的态度站起来，教育他们。","index":89,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"d9ffbd102a","type":"paragraph","text":"达：我们那里中国工人中有二百名党员，他们带领着其他工人很好地工作着。","index":90,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"9e35dd0933","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：好！工人一共有多少","index":91,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"6f75428852","type":"paragraph","text":"达：连家属一共一万三千人。过去的华侨一部分已回国，现在只剩下四五千人，但这些人都已年老了","index":92,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"5d4ff27e8e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：蒙古人指挥他们吗？","index":93,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"964adeff5b","type":"paragraph","text":"曾德：是的！蒙古人以主人翁的态度指挥着他们。","index":94,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"60f21fadfe","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：中国工人中有做木工活的吗","index":95,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"ab0a534377","type":"paragraph","text":"达：有。此外还有制砖的，以及其他各种行业。","index":96,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"4494c94886","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：让他们带蒙古徒弟吗","index":97,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"d90f5f8645","type":"paragraph","text":"达：他们分别地带着徒弟呢！","index":98,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"9bc0d2204e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：以后在农业方面，我们可以用人力援助你们，其数目可以是十万，也可以是二十万，甚至也可以达到三十万。其中某些人也可以帮助你们搞牧畜业。","index":99,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"3bf0e9d18a","type":"paragraph","text":"达：对，不过事先我们应该充分做好准备工作和计划工作。不然，接到那些人后，住宅等各方面要发生困难的。","index":100,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"e661d36444","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：对！应该逐步地进行这些工作。你们有八十万人口，因此可以发展农业、兴修水利了。","index":101,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"3648068477","type":"paragraph","text":"达：我们有五万二千多工人。","index":102,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"180f091264","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：八十万人口中有五方多工人，这数目不算小了。有使用机器的吗？","index":103,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"683aa7a6e9","type":"paragraph","text":"达：使用着半自动机器。","index":104,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"7757292830","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：有没有自动化的","index":105,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"8b24841c5d","type":"paragraph","text":"达：没有。","index":106,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"bfe08703ba","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：那么将来可以装置一些。关于这一问题，将来我们互相可以谈一谈。","index":107,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"b07d663d93","type":"paragraph","text":"达：由于你们的接助，我们现在有了火柴厂、瓷器厂，但火柴厂所需要的火柴盒等都是用手工制作。","index":108,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"cfdd3ebe60","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：火柴生产的数目多少","index":109,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"058c7274b8","type":"paragraph","text":"达：全国总共需要两千万盒火柴，明年生产可以达到这一数目。但在国内销路不太好。","index":110,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"40db269eb0","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：你们的市场怎样？","index":111,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"59cd87892b","type":"paragraph","text":"达：市场，有是有，但很小。","index":112,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"8562af9d41","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：今天我们谈得很好。","index":113,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"685079121c","type":"paragraph","text":"达：感谢您对我们的关怀，感谢您在百忙中抽出时间接见我们，感谢您对我们提出的具有重大意义的建议，感谢您对我们讲了很有益的话。我们回去后，把您今晚所讲的话，当做今后工作上的指针。当我们分手之际，我再一次代表我党中央和全体人民问您致襄心的敬意。","index":114,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"d511ef43f8","type":"paragraph","text":"二印发谈话记录的批语外交部：","index":115,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"51039496de","type":"paragraph","text":"这个谈话，应抄送我驻蒙使馆，内蒙自治区党委，及客省、市、区党委阅看，因为各省市区都有少数民族问题，另抄给统战部和民委党组。以上请会同尚昆同志办理”","index":116,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"c3a3620f8f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":117,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"},{"id":"486be0cdbd","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月十六日","index":118,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d"}],"page":{"id":"cb0adb094e","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2d19dd6b9d","start":47,"end":55}}}},"__N_SSG":true}